description: Use this operation to delete a human task user interface (worker task template). To see a list of human task user interfaces (work task templates) in your account, use ListHumanTaskUis. When you delete a worker task template, it no longer appears when you call ListHumanTaskUis.

parameters.name: HumanTaskUiName
parameters.description: The name of the human task user interface (work task template) you want to delete.
